拎出來講，唔會有人知，<br />\n根本冇乜人睇果篇報道。<br />\n耐不耐又要攞出嚟remind下大家。"},{"pid":"079209c73b26b767a83abb206871de1c0e3167a6","tid":2195281,"uid":39383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d39c02b8554dbc124b6d05bb1fade602fc6f378","tid":2195281,"uid":209024,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T05:30:50.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">原來所謂清白之身無賣xx係因為去左台灣黑警拉佢唔到。 咁陳同佳係台灣都無殺人啦</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T05:48:50.000Z","msg":"佳仔都係清白之驅, 一日未判, 佢都係無辜, 佢只係比人屈"},{"pid":"7facf3aaa3def7fe122c8cb8982af05ff20f8175","tid":2195281,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T05:49:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d242b6a3275219eef275677ed024b71cba602f5","tid":2195281,"uid":209024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T05:51:29.000Z","msg":"三十七年之後陳同佳就會係香港同人講佢係比人誣衊"},{"pid":"ae4a7422299a17031a5014f444c7253ca09bd396","tid":2195281,"uid":25468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T06:01:28.000Z","msg":"對港英法治無信心 ? 點解 97 後都返唔到黎 ?"},{"pid":"440635637208572a5c9e87714ddf158b48a13756","tid":2195281,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d242b6a3275219eef275677ed024b71cba602f5","tid":2195281,"uid":209024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T05:51:29.000Z","msg":"三十七年之後陳同佳就會係香港同人講佢係比人誣衊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T06:05:16.000Z","msg":"如果陳同佳死左<br />\n佢屋企人就可以話佢獲得平反<br />\n法律層面屬清白"},{"pid":"b2d65eae3c5c13c03ca669730c7f15e669f09dee","tid":2195281,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T06:06:41.000Z","msg":"不如問米問埋死係台灣既鹿惜珍有咩回應啦"},{"pid":"922b3602bebf7ad59693107f9ee1615b75aa3432","tid":2195281,"uid":2656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T06:06:49.000Z","msg":"在港共政府管治下，瀨共問題嚴重，手足對司法無信心，前往台灣而不返港是可以理解。手足都未被定罪，報道用「潛逃」兩字形容手足前往台灣，實屬不當。"},{"pid":"88e0ca968522dfae617e2849dc79617acc3e